oracle.adf.view.faces.bi.component.gantt
Class BackgroundBarFormat

java.lang.Object
  oracle.adf.view.faces.bi.component.gantt.BackgroundBarFormat
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class BackgroundBarFormat
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

A BackgroundBarFormat contains information about the appearance of a background bar. Application developers could specify the appearance of a new bar type or modify the appearance of an existing bar type by registering the BackgroundBarFormat with the TaskbarFormatManager.
